# StressAid environment variables (example)
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in values locally.
# NEVER commit real credentials. NEVER expose secrets in client code.
#
# No database, authentication, or third-party services are wired up in this
# foundation. The entries below are placeholders for future MVP work only and
# are intentionally left blank.

# --- Application ---
# Public base URL of the deployed app (used for absolute links/QR codes later).
# NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=

# --- Supabase (NOT USED YET) ---
# Reserved for future response storage. Prefer an EU region when configured.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
# Server-only key. Must never be exposed to the client bundle.
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=

# --- Teacher demo access (NOT USED YET) ---
# Reserved for future server-side teacher access. Never embed in client code.
# TEACHER_DEMO_ACCESS_CODE=
